<p><b>Baby Swimming</b><br />
<br />
We run <b>baby swim classes</b> and <b>toddler water confidence classes</b> across Yorkshire and Derbyshire, check out our pools to see if there is a suitable venue near you. All of our infant swim courses run in terms of 10 weeks duration and the cost includes a starter kit of an award booklet, essential happy nappy, 5 disposable swim nappies and Swimbabes swim bag. We currently have over 950 babies swimming with us each week.<br />
<br />
If you are interested in our <b>baby swimming classes</b> please do visit the &ldquo;<a href="index.php?main_page=page&amp;id=15">baby swimming</a>&rdquo; section for an overview. This also provides information on the benefits of baby swimming. <b>Baby swim classes</b> are suitable for babies from 1 month to 18 months of age and many of our existing swimmers have been on the programme for a couple of years. We do have a waiting list for our baby swimming programme so if you are interested please either complete the <a href="#">on-line registration form</a> or contact our office on 01484 683570 to join the waiting list.<br />
<br />
<b>Existing babies swimming with us</b><br />
If you are already on a baby swimming course with swim babes please do visit the <a href="http://index.php?main_page=news_archiv">news section</a> to see latest information about us , if you wish to pay for your new term you can now do so by clicking here. If you need a bigger size in you babies swim nappy or baby wetsuit please either let your teacher know or call us and we can bring your order along to your next lesson.<br />
<br />
<b>How do I get a photo of my baby swimming?</b><br />
When you join our swim programmes you will have the opportunity to join in our regular photo shoots. For our baby swimming stars we offer our stunning <b>Urchin Rock</b> shoot sessions 3 times a year. For more details see &ldquo;<a href="http://index.php?main_page=page&amp;id=17">photos</a>&rdquo;.<br />
<br />
<b>What do I need to take my baby swimming?</b><br />
Finally if you are taking your baby swimming for the first time check out our essential baby swim kits &ndash; they have everything you need for your baby whether they are swimming at the pool or on holiday.<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />
check our our best sellers, swim nappy, baby and toddler wetsuits and swim goggles. Our swim nappy is the splash about happy nappy - tried and tested it is certainly the best out there for avoiding embarrassing leaks. Our wetsuit range for baby from birth to toddlers and up to age 8 years offers a wide selection of styles and colours and is perfect for cool pools and holidays. Check out our swim goggles range by Zoggs, they are all great goggles with lots of adjustment and UV protections but our favourite swim goggles for all round durability is the little pro.<br />
